{"article_id":"uGny9wkke2SUuLYw","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"This image from the Twitter account of President Donald Trump shows a tweet","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"he posted on Friday , May 29 , 2020 ,","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"after protesters in Minneapolis torched a police station ,","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"capping three days of violent protests over the death of George Floyd ,","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"who pleaded for air","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"as a white police officer knelt on his neck .","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"The tweet drew a warning from Twitter for Trump 's rhetoric ,","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"with the social media giant saying","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"he had \" violated the Twitter Rules","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"about glorifying violence. \"","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"( Twitter via AP )","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"This image from the Twitter account of President Donald Trump shows a tweet","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"he posted on Friday , May 29 , 2020 ,","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"after protesters in Minneapolis torched a police station ,","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"capping three days of violent protests over the death of George Floyd ,","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"who pleaded for air","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"as a white police officer knelt on his neck .","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"The tweet drew a warning from Twitter for Trump 's rhetoric ,","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"with the social media giant saying","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"he had \" violated the Twitter Rules","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"about glorifying violence. \"","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"( Twitter via AP )","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"Twitter escalated tensions with President Donald Trump on Friday ,","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"adding a warning to one of his tweets for the first time","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"and saying","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"he violated the platform ' s rules","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"by glorifying violence","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"when he suggested","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"protesters in Minneapolis could be shot .","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"Trump has been railing against the company since earlier this week ,","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"when it for the first time applied fact checks to two of his tweets .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"Those were about mail-in ballots .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"The flap comes at a fraught moment for Twitter and social media more generally .","depth":4},{"id":33,"text":"Debate is heating up","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"about when and how much these companies should police the content on their platforms","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"as coronavirus misinformation swirls","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"and the 2020 U.S. presidential election looms .","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"For Trump , the feud with Twitter serves as a convenient distraction from major challenges","depth":5},{"id":38,"text":"he faces","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"heading into November ,","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"such as controlling a pandemic and dealing with soaring unemployment .","depth":4},{"id":41,"text":"The Trump tweet","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"that was flagged Friday","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"came amid days of violent protests over the death of George Floyd , a handcuffed black man","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"who pleaded for air","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"as a white police officer kneeled on his neck .","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"\" These THUGS are dishonoring the memory of George Floyd ,","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"and I won ' t let that happen , \"","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"Trump tweeted about the protesters .","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"\" Just spoke to Governor Tim Walz","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"and told him","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"that the Military is with him all the way .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"Any difficulty","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"and we will assume control","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"but , when the looting starts ,","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"the shooting starts .","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"Thank you ! \"","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"The comment evoked the civil-rights era","depth":5},{"id":58,"text":"by borrowing a phrase","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"used in 1967 by Miami ' s police chief","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"to warn of an aggressive police response to unrest in black neighborhoods .","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"Twitter did not remove the tweet ,","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"it had determined","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"it might be in the public interest to have it remain accessible .","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"But the tweet was hidden","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"so that a user","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"looking at Trump ' s timeline","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"would have to click on the warning","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"to see the original tweet .","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"Hiding it also effectively demotes the tweet","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"by limiting how users can retweet it","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"and ensuring that Twitter algorithms don ' t recommend it .","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"Twitter said Friday","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"it posted the warning label on Trump ' s tweet","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"\" based on the historical context of the last line , its connection to violence , and the risk","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"it could inspire similar actions today , \"","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"but left it up","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"\" given its relevance to ongoing matters of public importance . \"","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"A tweet","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"using the same language as Trump ' s","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"was later posted on the official White House Twitter account ,","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"and Twitter eventually put a warning on that too .","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"It was also posted on Facebook ,","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"which hasn ' t taken any visible action on it .","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"Twitter taking a harder line than Facebook on Trump ' s posts likely has something to do with Twitter ' s decision last year","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"to stop taking political ads ,","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"said Melissa Ryan , CEO of consultancy group Card Strategies ,","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"which researches online disinformation and right-wing extremism .","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"She said","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"the coronavirus pandemic has also led Twitter to inch toward stronger enforcement of its policies at the same time","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"that Trump ' s tweets have \" amped up in terms of crazy and intensity and disinformation . \"","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"\" Twitter and Trump have been playing a game of chicken , \"","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"Ryan said .","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"\" It feels like they ' ve both been moving toward this for a while . \"","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"Trump took to Twitter","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"to complain ,","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"calling multiple times for the revocation of Section 230 , part of a 1996 law","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"overhauling telecommunications .","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"That section generally protects social media platforms from liability for material","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"users post on their platforms .","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"Trump on Thursday signed an executive order","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"challenging those protections .","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"The order directs executive branch agencies to ask independent rule-making agencies","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"including the Federal Communications Commission and the Federal Trade Commission","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"to study","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"whether they can place new regulations on the companies ,","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"though experts express doubts","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"much can be done","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"without an act of Congress .","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"The president and fellow conservatives have claimed for years","depth":5},{"id":111,"text":"that Silicon Valley tech companies are biased against them .","depth":5},{"id":112,"text":"But there is no evidence for this ,","depth":5},{"id":113,"text":"and","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"while the executives and many employees of Twitter , Facebook and Google may lean liberal ,","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"the companies have stressed","depth":7},{"id":116,"text":"they have no business interest","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"in favoring one political party over the other .","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"Twitter first outlined in early 2018","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"that it wouldn ' t block world leaders from the platform","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"or remove their controversial tweets .","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"But it announced nearly a year ago","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"that it could apply warning labels and obscure the tweets of world leaders","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"if they used their accounts","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"to threaten or abuse others .","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"That followed complaints from Trump critics","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"that the president has gotten a free pass from Twitter","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"to post hateful messages and attack his enemies in ways","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"they say","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"could lead to violence .","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"Twitter further clarified its rules in October ,","depth":7},{"id":131,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"it will enforce its policies against any user","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"who makes clear and direct threats of violence against a person ,","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"but carving out an exception for government officials ' \" foreign policy saber-rattling on economic or military issues . \"","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"The earlier tweets","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"that Twitter flagged","depth":9},{"id":137,"text":"were not hidden","depth":8},{"id":138,"text":"but did come with an option","depth":8},{"id":139,"text":"to \" get the facts about mail-in ballots , \" a link","depth":9},{"id":140,"text":"that led to fact checks and news stories by media organizations .","depth":9},{"id":141,"text":"Those tweets called mail-in ballots \" fraudulent \"","depth":7},{"id":142,"text":"and predicted","depth":8},{"id":143,"text":"that \" mail boxes will be robbed , \" among other things .","depth":8},{"id":144,"text":"Twitter ' s decision","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"to flag Trump ' s tweets","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"came as the president continued to use the platform","depth":9},{"id":147,"text":"to push a debunked conspiracy theory","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"accusing MSNBC host and former congressman Joe Scarborough of killing a staffer in his Florida congressional office in 2001 .","depth":10},{"id":149,"text":"Medical officials determined","depth":10},{"id":150,"text":"the staffer had an undiagnosed heart condition ,","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"passed out","depth":12},{"id":152,"text":"and hit her head","depth":13},{"id":153,"text":"as she fell .","depth":13},{"id":154,"text":"Scarborough ,","depth":9},{"id":155,"text":"who was in Washington , not Florida , at the time ,","depth":9},{"id":156,"text":"has urged the president to stop his baseless attacks .","depth":8},{"id":157,"text":"The staffer ' s husband also recently demanded","depth":8},{"id":158,"text":"that Twitter remove the tweets .","depth":8},{"id":159,"text":"The company issued a statement","depth":9},{"id":160,"text":"expressing its regret to the husband","depth":9},{"id":161,"text":"but so far has taken no other action .","depth":8},{"id":162,"text":"Twitter ' s decision also likely will be seized upon outside the U.S.","depth":7},{"id":163,"text":"to scrutinize the social media behavior of other world leaders .","depth":7},{"id":164,"text":"Israel has been waging its own pressure campaign on the company","depth":9},{"id":165,"text":"over it allowing Iranian Supreme Leader Ayatollah Ali Khamenei to have an account .","depth":9},{"id":166,"text":"In a letter","depth":11},{"id":167,"text":"dated Sunday ,","depth":11},{"id":168,"text":"an Israeli official wrote to Twitter CEO Jack Dorsey","depth":10},{"id":169,"text":"complaining about Khamenei tweets","depth":10},{"id":170,"text":"that repeated comments","depth":11},{"id":171,"text":"he made in a recent speech in support of Palestinians","depth":12},{"id":172,"text":"that called Israel a \" cancerous growth \"","depth":13},{"id":173,"text":"that will be \" uprooted and destroyed . \"","depth":13},{"id":174,"text":"On the other hand , the company has removed tweets","depth":11},{"id":175,"text":"related to the coronavirus","depth":11},{"id":176,"text":"from the leaders of Brazil and Venezuela ,","depth":10},{"id":177,"text":"and says","depth":10},{"id":178,"text":"it will remove content","depth":11},{"id":179,"text":"that has a call to action","depth":12},{"id":180,"text":"that poses a threat to people ' s health or well being .","depth":12},{"id":181,"text":"It has also previously used the warning label for an elected official , Brazilian politician Osmar Terra ,","depth":9},{"id":182,"text":"who tweeted","depth":10},{"id":183,"text":"that quarantine increases the spread of the virus .","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":367,"left":224,"right":366,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":224,"left":215,"right":223,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":215,"left":194,"right":214,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":194,"left":189,"right":193,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":189,"left":0,"right":188,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":188,"left":185,"right":187,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":185,"left":1,"right":2,"relation